{"tid":918701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BDSM俱樂部被查　金髮皮衣妹趴地畫面曝光","createTime":"2018-11-27T12:10:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T16:41:57.000Z","uid":32511,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5e6d3a733e13e66a153c5c01c94cbdc720999620","tid":918701,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T12:10:52.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯一間BDSM俱樂部被搜查，現場許多金髮妹身穿膠皮衣趴在地上的畫面也因此曝光。據俄羅斯《Life》報導，頓河畔羅斯托夫一間皮繩愉虐（BDSM）俱樂部，有數十名男女參加，日前遭到警方搜查，而內部的照片影片也隨之曝光，數十名身穿膠皮衣、網襪、兔女郎的女子，全部趴在地上接受盤查，至於警方到底是去做啥，羅斯托夫警方並沒有說明。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjAoxz2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxjAoxz2.png&h=eaa8ec8b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OgnNZe3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOgnNZe3.png&h=ba5328cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7b465d10f23a910b761735c8914a3e754000529","tid":918701,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T12:11:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd8a51b707444e3403f752af1a83ad8645d50da","tid":918701,"uid":24007,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T12:12:29.000Z","msg":"報名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e179dbb9061899142ea433604759db7d57145d1","tid":918701,"uid":49258,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T12:12:37.000Z","msg":"堆屎忽好正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db184bfc6149acb3abbe91674d9d2e31e71826ec","tid":918701,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T12:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fa